{"title":"Gold dragon scale mail","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Gold_dragon_scale_mail","type":"markdown","data":"| \\[   gold dragon scale mail   |                                                |\n| ----------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |\n| Appearance                    | gold dragon scale mail                         |\n|                               |                                                |\n| Slot                          | [body armor](/wiki/Body_armor \"Body armor\")    |\n| AC                            | [9](/wiki/Armor_class \"Armor class\")           |\n| Special                       | - radius 2-4 [light](/wiki/Light \"Light\")      |\n|                               |                                                |\n| Base price                    | 1200 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")             |\n| Weight                        | [40](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")                    |\n| Material                      | [dragon hide](/wiki/Dragon_hide \"Dragon hide\") |\n\n*The following information pertains to an upcoming version ([NetHack 3.7.0](/wiki/NetHack_3.7.0 \"NetHack 3.7.0\")). If this version is now released, please verify that it is still accurate, then update the page to incorporate this information.*\n\nGold dragons, gold dragon scales, and gold dragon scale mail are added.\n\n**Gold dragon scale mail**, is a type of [dragon scale mail](/wiki/Dragon_scale_mail \"Dragon scale mail\"). It emits [light](/wiki/Light \"Light\") when worn, in a radius dependent on [beatitude](/wiki/Beatitude \"Beatitude\"): 2 if cursed, 3 if uncursed, and 4 if blessed. Notably, this is the only way in the game to obtain a permanent source of radius 4 light. They also provide [hallucination resistance](/wiki/Hallucination_resistance \"Hallucination resistance\").\n\nGold dragon scale mail can be produced from [gold dragon scales](/wiki/Gold_dragon_scales \"Gold dragon scales\"), which might be dropped by a [gold dragon](/wiki/Gold_dragon \"Gold dragon\").\n\nNote that \"GDSM\" may be used to describe gold dragon scale mail, but more likely refers to [gray dragon scale mail](/wiki/Gray_dragon_scale_mail \"Gray dragon scale mail\").\n\n### SlashTHEM\n\nSlashTHEM introduces golden dragon scale mail, which provides [sickness resistance](/wiki/Immunity_to_sickness \"Immunity to sickness\"). Golden dragon scale mail emits light of radius 2.\n\n## See also\n\n- [Dragon scale mail](/wiki/Dragon_scale_mail \"Dragon scale mail\") for more detailed information on what makes dragon scale mail special and how to obtain it.\n\n[Template:Nethack-370](/index.php?title=Template:Nethack-370\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"Template:Nethack-370 (page does not exist)\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Gold dragon scale mail - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Gold_dragon_scale_mail\",\"wgTitle\":\"Gold dragon scale mail\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":154622,\"wgRevisionId\":154622,\"wgArticleId\":37646,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Upcoming\",\"Dragon armor\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\