ay in the game to obtain a permanent source of radius 4 light. They also provide hallucination resistance.\"/>\n<link rel=\"image_src\" href=\"/images/6/65/Nethackwiki-logo.png\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Gold_dragon_scale_mail\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Gold_dragon_scale_mail rootpage-Gold_dragon_scale_mail skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Gold dragon scale mail</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-yellow\">[</span> &#8194; gold dragon scale mail &#8194;\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td>gold dragon scale mail\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Slot\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Body_armor\" title=\"Body armor\">body armor</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>AC\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Armor_class\" title=\"Armor class\">9</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Special\n</th>\n<td><ul><li>radius 2-4 <a href=\"/wiki/Light\" title=\"Light\">light</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>1200 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">40</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Material\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_hide\" title=\"Dragon hide\">dragon hide</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"upcoming\">\n<p><i>The following information pertains to an upcoming version (<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.7.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.7.0\">NetHack 3.7.0</a>). If this version is now released, please verify that it is still accurate, then update the page to incorporate this information.</i>\n</p>\nGold dragons, gold dragon scales, and gold dragon scale mail are added.</div>\n<p><b>Gold dragon scale mail</b>, is a type of <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_scale_mail\" title=\"Dragon scale mail\">dragon scale mail</a>. It emits <a href=\"/wiki/Light\" title=\"Light\">light</a> when worn, in a radius dependent on <a href=\"/wiki/Beatitude\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Beatitude\">beatitude</a>: 2 if cursed, 3 if uncursed, and 4 if blessed. Notably, this is the only way in the game to obtain a permanent source of radius 4 light. They also provide <a href=\"/wiki/Hallucination_resistance\" title=\"Hallucination resistance\">hallucination resistance</a>.\n</p><p>Gold dragon scale mail can be produced from <a href=\"/wiki/Gold_dragon_scales\" title=\"Gold dragon scales\">gold dragon scales</a>, which might be dropped by a <a href=\"/wiki/Gold_dragon\" title=\"Gold dragon\">gold dragon</a>.\n</p><p>Note that \"GDSM\" may be used to describe gold dragon scale mail, but more likely refers to <a href=\"/wiki/Gray_dragon_scale_mail\" title=\"Gray dragon scale mail\">gray dragon scale mail</a>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</span></h3>\n<p>SlashTHEM introduces golden dragon scale mail, which provides <a href=\"/wiki/Immunity_to_sickness\" title=\"Immunity to sickness\">sickness resistance</a>. Golden dragon scale mail emits light of radius 2.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_scale_mail\" title=\"Dragon scale mail\">Dragon scale mail</a> for more detailed information on what makes dragon scale mail special and how to obtain it.</li></ul>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template:Nethack-370&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template:Nethack-370 (page does not exist)\">Template:Nethack-370</a>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926183841\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 75/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 417/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 938/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 277/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   10.193      1 -total\n 78.46%    7.997      1 Template:Armor\n 50.36%    5.133      1 Template:Autotile\n 37.21%    3.793      1 Template:LinklessExists\n 12.17%    1.240      1 Template:Upcoming\n 11.14%    1.136      1 Template:Yellow\n  7.15%    0.729      1 Template:Nethack-370\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:37646-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926183841 and revision id 154622\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Go