teargumentsize\":{\"value\":277,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":10,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":1,\"limit\":100},\"unstrip-depth\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":20},\"unstrip-size\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":5000000},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   10.193      1 -total\",\" 78.46%    7.997      1 Template:Armor\",\" 50.36%    5.133      1 Template:Autotile\",\" 37.21%    3.793      1 Template:LinklessExists\",\" 12.17%    1.240      1 Template:Upcoming\",\" 11.14%    1.136      1 Template:Yellow\",\"  7.15%    0.729      1 Template:Nethack-370\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926183841\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":51});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{armor\n  |color=yellow\n  |name=gold dragon scale mail\n  |slot=body armor\n  |ac=9\n  |special=<ul><li>radius 2-4 [[light]]</li></ul>\n  |cost=1200\n  |weight=40\n  |material=dragon hide\n}}\n{{upcoming|NetHack 3.7.0|Gold dragons, gold dragon scales, and gold dragon scale mail are added.}}\n'''Gold dragon scale mail''', is a type of [[dragon scale mail]]. It emits [[light]] when worn, in a radius dependent on [[beatitude]]: 2 if cursed, 3 if uncursed, and 4 if blessed. Notably, this is the only way in the game to obtain a permanent source of radius 4 light. They also provide [[hallucination resistance]].\n\nGold dragon scale mail can be produced from [[gold dragon scales]], which might be dropped by a [[gold dragon]].\n\nNote that \"GDSM\" may be used to describe gold dragon scale mail, but more likely refers to [[gray dragon scale mail]].\n\n===SlashTHEM===\nSlashTHEM introduces golden dragon scale mail, which provides [[immunity to sickness|sickness resistance]]. Golden dragon scale mail emits light of radius 2.\n\n==See also==\n\n*[[Dragon scale mail]] for more detailed information on what makes dragon scale mail special and how to obtain it.\n\n[[Category:Dragon armor]]\n{{nethack-370}}"}